Scope of this license
======================

The MIT license above applies to the NEW code authored for OpenLaszlo 5.0 —
principally the TypeScript LZX->DHTML compiler (`compiler/src`, the built
`compiler/dist` and `compiler/lzc-browser.js`), the static bootstrap and
Service Worker (`index.html`, `service-worker.js`), and other 5.0-original
tooling and glue.

This repository also bundles components from the original OpenLaszlo 4.x
platform — including the DHTML runtime (`runtime/`), original documentation
(`docs/`), and original LZX example sources — which are
Copyright (c) 2001-2010 Laszlo Systems, Inc. and remain licensed under the
Common Public License Version 1.0 (CPL 1.0), the license under which
OpenLaszlo was originally released. Those terms continue to govern that
original material; see https://www.openlaszlo.org and the original LPS
distribution for the full CPL text.
